Veggie Burger

25 min
$5
350 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

Egg

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianHigh ProteinGluten Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main Dish

Tags:

Description

A flavorful, hearty veggie burger packed with nutrients and deliciousness, perfect for a quick meal!

Ingredients

  • black beans, canned: 1 can (15 oz)
  • oats: 1/2 cup
  • bell pepper, chopped: 1/2 cup
  • onion, chopped: 1/4 cup
  • garlic, minced: 2 cloves
  • egg: 1
  • cumin: 1 tsp
  • salt: 1/2 tsp
  • pepper: 1/4 tsp
  • olive oil: 2 tbsp
  • burger buns: 2
  • lettuce: 2 leaves
  • tomato, sliced: 1
